DATA

AREA 956 KM2 (2010), FOREST 777, CULTIVATED 61; COUNTY = FUTAMI [\u4E8C
\u6D77]; POP 18,896 (2010), 23,781 (1990 - YAKUMO 18,872, KUMAISHI 
