NOTE 

#1  Among the northern tip, southern tip, eastern tip, and western tip 
of Hokkaidou island, the western tip is the most difficult to visit.  
It is a steep cliff at Cape Obana.
	Including small islands, the western tip is Oshima-ooshima 
island in Matsumae Town, Oshima sub-prefecture.  It is an uninhabited 
island. 
	Oota Shrine at Cape Obana is one of the oldest shrines in 
